  m_Name: DefenseMinistryEvent
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WarForOilEvent
  id: wfo_wtetwc_02
  displayName: The Minister of Defense wants to end the war.
  description: "Rising casualties and political pressure have pushed peace talks
    to the table. You can sabotage the process, accelerate it, or quietly steer it
    for your own gain \u2014 but every move will shift your Wealth, Suspicion, and
    Trust balance."
  devNote: "Mafya skilleri olu\u015Fturulunca se\xE7eneklere eklenecek\nR\xFC\u015Fvet
    Skilleri olu\u015Fturulunca eklenecek se\xE7eneklere"
  eventNote: "Savunma bakan\u0131 sava\u015F\u0131 bitirmek ister, oyuncu isteklerine
    g\xF6re choice lar ile durumu y\xF6netmeye \xE7al\u0131\u015F\u0131r.\r\n\r\nilk
    se\xE7enek savunma bakan\u0131yla anla\u015Fmaya \xE7al\u0131\u015Fmakt\u0131r.
    probabilistic end war devreye girer. war supportuyla orant\u0131l\u0131 bir \u015Fekilde
    belli olas\u0131l\u0131klarda ya ayn\u0131 event tekrar tetiklenir ya bakan sava\u015F\u0131
    bitirmemeye ikna olur ya da dinlemez ve sava\u015F bitirilir. inspectordaki de\u011Ferler
    war support = 50 olan biri i\xE7in ge\xE7erlidir war support artt\u0131k\xE7a
    savunma bakan\u0131 ikna olmaya meyillenir.\n\nikinci se\xE7enek bar\u0131\u015F\u0131
    sa\u011Flamakt\u0131r oyun h\u0131zl\u0131ca ate\u015Fkese ba\u011Flan\u0131r.\n\n\xFC\xE7\xFCnc\xFC
    se\xE7enek g\xF6revden almakt\u0131r siyasi n\xFCfuz gerekir\n\nd\xF6rd\xFCnc\xFC
    se\xE7enek \xF6ld\xFCrmektir mafya skilli gerekir. \xF6ld\xFCr\xFCl\xFCrse bir
    sonraki eventte protest ba\u015Flama ihtimali %30 artar\n\n\nbe\u015Finci se\xE7enek
    r\xFC\u015Fvetlemektir \"b\xFCy\xFCk ihtimalle\" ve daha az \u015F\xFCpheyle
    ikna eder"
